{"tid":1005701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【印尼】明打威群島6.1級淺層地震　無觸發海嘯警報","createTime":"2019-02-02T11:54:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T11:54:56.000Z","uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"06a5ca0702c896e93e0b7b7c3d3099aba2a0351a","tid":1005701,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T11:54:43.000Z","msg":"明打威群島6.1級淺層地震　無觸發海嘯警報<br />\n<br />\n印尼西部明打威群島於當地時間周六（2日）下午約5時30分，發生黎克特制6.1級淺層地震，震源深度達10公里，沒有觸發海嘯警報，亦暫未收到傷亡及損毀報告。<br />\n<br />\n美國地質勘探局數據顯示，地震震央位於西蘇門答臘外海，位於主要港口城市巴東以南約200公里。有巴東居民憶述，事發時震感強烈、房子搖晃，是同日第二次感受到地震，大驚之下跑到戶外暫避。"},{"pid":"fdafe9727cfa7bb175d8c94cbd3a542448d663c6","tid":1005701,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T11:54:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190202/mobile/bkn-20190202184134723-0202_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190202%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190202184134723-0202_00912_001.html&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2VGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=80159ce4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190202/mobile/bkn-20190202184134723-0202_00912_001.html</a>"}]}